modules.description: Tracks and analyzes numerical data distributions with high resolution. It supports operations like recording values, calculating percentiles, and merging histograms. Works with numeric types and accumulates data for performance monitoring or statistical analysis.

Tracks and analyzes numerical value distributions by recording individual integers and calculating statistical metrics. Operates on a custom type `t` representing a histogram structure, supporting operations like percentile lookup, min/max retrieval, and statistical computation. Used to monitor performance metrics, such as response times, by capturing and analyzing value frequencies.
